{"tid":1698133,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【聖誕上映】甄子丹隨心去演 《葉問4：完結篇》最後一戰","createTime":"2019-11-07T09:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T04:25:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"df8b2997a1b4482a38900a97718ded9e06300306","tid":1698133,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"甄子丹主演、葉偉信導演、黃百鳴監製的功夫電影《葉問》系列創出十年經典，一直都有票房保證，而《葉問4：完結篇》最後一戰，落實於聖誕檔期上映。甄子丹和葉偉信合作無間，充滿默契，今集甄子丹選擇隨心方法去演，他說：「去到第四集，我已經好了解『葉問』這個人物，導演亦想我隨心一啲，所以都係開拍前兩天先畀劇本我，再結合現場畀我嘅感覺琢磨，結果演出來嘅效果，我同導演都好滿意。」<br />\n<br />\n首條預告片中，看到年少曾經在英文學校讀書的葉問，以簡單英語回答外籍校長提問，帶出今集故事以外國為背景。繼而葉問與飾演中華總會會長萬宗華的吳樾大打出手，二人以玻璃轉盤切磋武術；同時看到葉問與曾參演《奇異博士》的英國動作演員Scott Adkins飾演的海軍陸戰隊軍官，在軍營對決，同樣新加入的吳建豪就飾演華籍軍官、飾演李小龍的陳國坤在體育館打跆拳道；還有在唐人街中秋晚會挑戰葉問的高戰（Chris Collins）及飾演被欺凌的華人女學生、年僅16歲的新生代演員李宛妲，短短分半鐘《葉問4》預告戲味十足。<br />\n<br />\n其實《葉問》系列能橫誇十年，今集葉問為了兒子前途，遠赴美國尋找學校；人在異鄉，生活非想像外，葉問亦見證了華人被歧視，導演葉偉信說：「每次葉問出手，都因為睇到不公義，呢個係葉問武之初心，從來冇變，今集更想帶出，無論你喺邊，只要自己係爭氣、自強，邊度都美滿幸福。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191107/large/1573117408_eadc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191107%2Flarge%2F1573117408_eadc.jpg&h=9ef2c35e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191107/60241350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191107%2F60241350&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=1f4d7210\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191107%2F60241350&h=21d03de4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191107/60241350</a>"},{"pid":"333cf28e7ddfe0b865423d28ddf884af34f3dd6f","tid":1698133,"uid":156096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:49:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，<span style=\"color: red;\">不推post</span> &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先45%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=9136bb22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"aeb2969d917549a4c51e46b0e1226d68f53d94e8","tid":1698133,"uid":4917,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"甄子丹、陳國坤舐共舐到雪雪聲，不了"},{"pid":"5b12bbb127def22d5de7bbab950824abcc3efa5c","tid":1698133,"uid":124439,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"真心覺得飛機油十足 只有香港導演先至拍到呢種春味起機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5541d52200186fd30ff17ee714b13c50127263c7","tid":1698133,"uid":31637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌"},{"pid":"14bb025039d3386cbd94e303ebb8ddc281efd0de","tid":1698133,"uid":274435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10